<br>
Don't forget bolt misses / blocks.  Even the best mages can expect at the minimum a 1 in 50 bolt miss ratio due to forces out of their control.  That's a 2% reduction in dpm / dps (over time).  <br>
<br>
I believe its reasonable to expect about a 5% miss / block rate.  If you check the DD chart sticky you can see a pretty large discussion regarding this topic.<br>
